text: Le Bû-sur-Rouvres (, literally Le Bû on Rouvres) is a commune in the Calvados department in the Normandy region in northwestern France. ==Population== ==See also== *Communes of the Calvados department ==References== Category:Communes of Calvados (department) Category:Calvados communes articles needing translation from French Wikipedia
